data.description: Seller is offering $10,000 in buyer concessions with for buyer to use for closing costs, interest rate buy-down or price reduction!  beautiful 6-bedroom, executive home is located in one of the most desirable, gated communities in Dacula's Archer High School District. Sitting on a large corner lot, this spacious home checks all the boxes. The main floor's open concept boasts hardwood floors throughout. The foyer welcomes you into a view of the formal dining room. The chef's kitchen is perfect for entertaining with double ovens, a gas cooktop and a large eat-in island with beautiful granite counters.  The kitchen overlooks the family room with fireplace. The owner's suite completes the first floor and is truly a retreat with plenty of space as well as an ample walk-in closet and a bathroom with double vanities, granite counters and separate tub and shower.  The second floor welcomes you into the space with a large loft area, perfect for a media room or flex space.  5 additional bedrooms surround the loft space and complete the upper level. One of the home's most impressive features is the fully screened and enclosed patio off the kitchen and family room, perfect for entertaining.     GPS using address: 3379 Ridge Manor Way!
